@startuml
actor Pembeli
boundary View
control CheckoutController
entity OrderModel
database Database
participant "API RajaOngkir" as RajaOngkir

Pembeli -> View: Buka Keranjang & Lanjut Checkout
View -> CheckoutController: GET /checkout
CheckoutController --> View: Tampilkan Halaman Checkout

Pembeli -> View: Pilih Alamat Pengiriman
View -> CheckoutController: POST /checkout/ongkir
CheckoutController -> RajaOngkir: API POST /cost (alamat, berat)
RajaOngkir --> CheckoutController: Response Tarif Ekspedisi
CheckoutController --> View: Kembalikan Pilihan Kurir & Harga JSON

Pembeli -> View: Pilih Kurir
View -> View: Hitung Total Bayar via JavaScript
Pembeli -> View: Klik Buat Pesanan
View -> CheckoutController: POST /checkout/store (cart, kurir)
CheckoutController -> OrderModel: createOrder(cart, courier)
OrderModel -> Database: INSERT orders
Database --> OrderModel: OK
OrderModel --> CheckoutController: Order object
CheckoutController --> View: Redirect Halaman Pembayaran
@enduml